  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1441500/extras/7ee4345c439ea9b094f6a7fe110441b5.poster.avif?t=1771178906\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1441500/extras/7ee4345c439ea9b094f6a7fe110441b5.webm?t=1771178906\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1441500/extras/7ee4345c439ea9b094f6a7fe110441b5.mp4?t=1771178906\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traceur's Dreamlab is - as the name implies - a place to be for every parkour runner!<br>You can build your own levels, including not only challenging obstacles but also tricky puzzles and share them with the community. Within our multiplayer system you can run against your friends and other online players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1441500/extras/c68674af496983a8e676b6bffb2e0cc6.poster.avif?t=1771178906\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1441500/extras/c68674af496983a8e676b6bffb2e0cc6.webm?t=1771178906\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1441500/extras/c68674af496983a8e676b6bffb2e0cc6.mp4?t=1771178906\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique leveleditor</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Live Multiplayer - Run against your friends in real time</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online leaderboards (currently disabled)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ingame workshop support for level sharing</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tricky puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenging parkours</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A bunch of Premade Levels</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1441500/extras/06669a7686289e7d9d716f4d7db3c42a.poster.avif?t=1771178906\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1441500/extras/06669a7686289e7d9d716f4d7db3c42a.webm?t=1771178906\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1441500/extras/06669a7686289e7d9d716f4d7db3c42a.mp4?t=1771178906\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
